---
title: Quick Herbed Double Beef & Apple Salad Bowl  with Croutons & Creamy Pesto
description: If you’re craving a salad but worried it won’t fill you up, this is the one to go for. Tender, herby beef strips are tossed through a mix of crunchy cucumber, fresh salad leaves and sweet apple. It even has chunks of toasted panini mixed through so you don’t have to miss out on your carb fix!
